		<part id="a-to-b">
			<title>From A to B</title>
			<slide id="execution">
				<title>API Strategy Execution</title>
				<ul>
					<li>Typical questions when going from A to B</li>
					<ul>
						<li>A: Where are we starting?</li>
						<li>B: Where do we want to go?</li>
						<li>Progress: How far along are we?</li>
					</ul>
					<li>Digital transformation is no waterfall and never ends</li>
					<ul>
						<li>Start: Identify priorities, make small steps, and reassess often</li>
						<li>Goal: Minimizing the time from ideation to production</li>
						<li>Progress: Listen to teams, identify bottlenecks, and provide support</li>
					</ul>
				</ul>
			</slide>
