			<title>Conclusions</title>
			<slide id="api-conclusions">
				<title>Necessary, but not Sufficient</title>
				<img src="services-cycle.png" title="Digital Transformation Pillars" style="float: right ; width : 30% ; margin : 0% 5% 5% 5% ; "/>
				<ul>
					<li>APIs are necessary, but not sufficient for digital transformation</li>
					<li>APIs are most effective when there is a continuously managed API landscape</li>
					<li>The Catalyst's only mission is to improve customer success</li>
